@startuml
title ArcHub CMS - Package Promotion Application Service
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

actor "Editor / release manager" as Editor
component "Package admin routes\n/export /inspect /plan /import" as Routes
component "ArcHubPackageService\napplication.packages" as Packages
component "ArcHubDomainEvent" as Event
component "ArcHubCMSService\ncompatibility API" as CMS
database "SQLite CMS store" as DB
component "Future promotion handlers\nsigning, audit, rollback,\nexternal environments" as Handlers

Editor --> Routes : package request
Routes --> Packages : export / inspect\nplan_import / import_package
Packages --> CMS : existing package methods
CMS --> DB : content model, nodes,\nmedia, domains, workflows
Packages --> Event : package.exported\npackage.import.planned\npackage.imported
Event ..> Handlers : future integration boundary
Packages --> Routes : compatible JSON payload
@enduml
